TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: WITH calendar_dates AS (SELECT hbi_fiscal_calendar.week_begin_date AS week_begin_date FROM hbi_fiscal_calendar WHERE TRUNC(SYSDATE) = hbi_fiscal_calendar.calendar_date ), minShipDate AS (SELECT a.style_Cd, a.color_cd, a.attribute_Cd, a.size_Cd, a.location_id, MIN(SHIPMENT_DUE_DATE) AS Ship_date FROM ibp_demand a INNER JOIN hbi_fiscal_calendar hfc ON a.SHIPMENT_DUE_DATE = hfc.CALENDAR_DATE INNER JOIN hbi_fiscal_calendar hfc1 ON TRUNC(sysdate) = hfc1.CALENDAR_DATE WHERE a.key_figure_name = 'RECOMMENDEDSAFETYSTOCK' AND a.SHIPMENT_DUE_DATE > hfc1.week_end_date AND a.quantity > 0 AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM ibp_demand b INNER JOIN hbi_fiscal_calendar hfc3 ON b.SHIPMENT_DUE_DATE = hfc3.week_begin_date AND TRUNC(sysdate) = hfc3.CALENDAR_DATE WHERE b.key_figure_name = 'RECOMMENDEDSAFETYSTOCK' AND a.product_id = b.product_id AND a.location_id = b.location_id AND b.quantity > 0) GROUP BY a.style_Cd, a.color_cd, a.attribute_Cd, a.size_Cd, a.location_id ) SELECT IBD.AS_OF_DATE, IBD.KEY_FIGURE_NAME, IBD.PRODUCT_ID, IBD.STYLE_CD, IBD.COLOR_CD, IBD.ATTRIBUTE_CD, IBD.SIZE_CD, IBD.QUANTITY, IBD.STOCKING_CATEGORY, IBD.PLANNING_LEAD_TIME, IBD.TARGET_SERVICE_LEVEL, IBD.LOCATION_ID, IBD.MATERIAL_TYPE_ID, IBD.SHIPMENT_DUE_DATE, (SELECT week_begin_date FROM calendar_dates ) AS ALIAS_WEEK_BEGIN_DATE FROM ibp_Demand IBD INNER JOIN minShipDate MSD ON MSD.style_Cd = IBD.style_Cd AND MSD.color_cd = IBD.color_cd AND MSD.attribute_Cd = IBD.attribute_Cd AND MSD.size_Cd = IBD.size_Cd AND MSD.Ship_date = IBD.SHIPMENT_DUE_DATE AND IBD.location_id = MSD.location_id WHERE ibd.key_figure_name = 'RECOMMENDEDSAFETYSTOCK' AND IBD.quantity > 0

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Optional lookup to get the alias lead time from MFG_PATH x MFG_PATH_CHP join
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP2_MFG_PATH_LEADTIME

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CASE NVL(MPC.MFG_PATH_ID, '0') WHEN '0' THEN (CASE MP.MAKE_OR_BUY_CD WHEN 'B' THEN TO_NUMBER($$PARM_BUY_LEAD_TIME) ELSE TO_NUMBER($$PARM_MAKE_LEAD_TIME) END) ELSE (MPC.LEAD_TIME * 7) END AS ALIAS_LEAD_TIME, MP.STYLE_CD AS STYLE_CD, MP.COLOR_CD AS COLOR_CD, MP.ATTRIBUTE_CD AS ATTRIBUTE_CD, MP.SIZE_CD AS SIZE_CD FROM MFG_PATH MP LEFT JOIN MFG_PATH_CHP MPC ON (MP.STYLE_CD = MPC.STYLE_CD AND MP.COLOR_CD = MPC.COLOR_CD AND MP.ATTRIBUTE_CD = MPC.ATTRIBUTE_CD AND MP.SIZE_CD = MPC.SIZE_CD AND MP.MFG_PATH_ID = MPC.MFG_PATH_ID AND MP.REVISION_NO = MPC.REVISION_NO) WHERE MP.CORP_STD_PATH_IND = 'Y'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_CD = I_ALIAS_STYLE_CD AND COLOR_CD = I_ALIAS_COLOR_CD AND ATTRIBUTE_CD = I_ALIAS_ATTRIBUTE_CD AND SIZE_CD = I_ALIAS_SIZE_CD
